Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快开门，橄榄石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Open the door, Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.44,0:00:32.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果“融合簇”真的置我们于危险之中\N{\fnArial\fs48}If this "cluster" is putting us in danger,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.86,0:00:35.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你得告诉我们那是什么，这样我们才能阻止它\N{\fnArial\fs48}you need to tell us what it is so we can stop it.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不！我讨厌你们\N{\fnArial\fs48}No! I hate you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我才不告诉你们融合簇的任何信息呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not telling you anything about the cluster.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，搞毛\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.71,0:00:45.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是像一大团，呃，即食麦片吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is it like a big, uh, hunk of granola?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.98,0:00:47.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么是即食麦片？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's granola?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.64,0:00:49.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我很确定那不是即食麦片\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sure it's not granola.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着，橄榄石，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now, Peridot,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.08,0:00:53.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我确定我们能达成一定共识\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sure we can reach some sort of agreement.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许我们来做个交易？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Perhaps a trade is in order?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.06,0:00:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，真好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.05,0:00:58.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么不给我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why don't you just give me back
Dialogue: 100,0:00:58.15,0:01:00.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的腿部和臂部增强器？\N{\fnArial\fs48}my leg enhancements and my arm attachments
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.13,0:01:02.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}外加我的显示屏和日志和所有的信息？\N{\fnArial\fs48}with my screen and my log and all my information.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.73,0:01:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，等等，你毁了它们！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, wait, you destroyed them!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以，不，我不认为我们能达成某种共识！\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, no, I don't think we can reach some sort of agreement!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.35,0:01:13.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，橄榄石，你可以转身了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, Peridot, you can turn around now.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.04,0:01:19.41,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很抱歉打断你们的审讯\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry for interrupting your interrogation.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.53,0:01:20.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不要担心，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry about it, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.97,0:01:24.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我发誓，橄榄石随时都会招供的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I swear, Peridot is gonna crack any second now.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我永远不会像你们招供的，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll never crack for the likes of you,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们这群...水晶草包！\N{\fnArial\fs48}you...Crystal clods.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.66,0:01:32.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦～，你的草包们可就在门口，你个小-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ooh, I got your clods right here, you little --
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}hold on, Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果她不愿意提供任何帮助的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}If she's not gonna be of any help.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我们自己来调查这件事\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's investigate this thing on our own.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.75,0:01:37.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会跟你一起做的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.84,0:01:38.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.91,0:01:40.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们需要你呆在家里\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're gonna need you to stay here
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看管我们的...贵宾\N{\fnArial\fs48}and keep an eye on our...Guest.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.22,0:01:46.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对，确保她不会搞幺蛾子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. Make sure she doesn't try anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.42,0:01:47.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.11,0:01:49.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她失去肢端增强器后没什么威胁\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's harmless without her limb enhancers
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我才不是毫无威胁呢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not harmless!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:50.86,0:01:52.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，给我闭嘴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, hush up!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.35,0:01:53.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有一件事我得提\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's one more thing I have to mention.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.24,0:01:55.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.71,0:01:58.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我爱你，拜拜\N{\fnArial\fs48}I love you. Bye.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.28,0:02:00.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}待会见\N{\fnArial\fs48}See ya later.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.86,0:02:09.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你得知道，她们走了，你现在可以出来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}They left, you know. You can come out now.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.46,0:02:11.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，我-我喜欢在里面\N{\fnArial\fs48}No. I-I like it in here.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，看来真要下雨了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow. It's really coming down.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.15,0:02:26.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}开始了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's happening!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.51,0:02:26.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.06,0:02:28.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}-融合簇！\N{\fnArial\fs48}-The cluster!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.62,0:02:29.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有什么能制造那么恐怖的-\N{\fnArial\fs48}What else could be making that horrible --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.48,0:02:34.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊！它在内部拍击着地球\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! It's pounding on the earth from the inside.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是世界末日了\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is it. This is the end of the world.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，那只是闪电而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, that's just thunder.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.93,0:02:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错，一切都还正常\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, everything is fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那只是闪电，跟着雨一起出现\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's just thunder. It happens when it rains.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Eh...Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不知道雨？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't know about rain?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}离开我的屏幕，我什么都不知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know anything without my screen.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这没什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看，假设汤是大海\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here, pretend this soup is the ocean.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.77,0:02:57.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当太阳加热汤时，\N{\fnArial\fs48}When the sun warms it up,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.06,0:03:00.21,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}水被蒸发，形成云\N{\fnArial\fs48}the water evaporates into clouds,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.21,0:03:00.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就如同这蒸汽\N{\fnArial\fs48}like this steam.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而当云变得非常重时，就开始下雨了\N{\fnArial\fs48}And when the clouds get really heavy, it rains.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以滚烫的液体从天上倾泻而下？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So scalding liquid pours down from the sky?
